gongluck's blog https://gongluck.github.io/cpp/badapple-console/ -<p>有屏幕的地方就有BadApple!在B站看过好多版本,于是我也用控制台做了一个。网上很多人都是直接显示bmp图片的,但我这个版本是用libvlc实时解码和播放的,音频用libvlc播放,画面就是转换成字符后输出到控制台。除了BadApple这种黑白动画,也能播放彩色视频。具体可以看一下效果视频。</p>
<h3 id="设计思路">设计思路</h3>
<p>libvlc解码转码出RGBA和播放音频，再将RGBA量化为黑('*')白(&rsquo; &lsquo;)两个颜色并输出到屏幕。</p>
<h3 id="效果视频">效果视频</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1N64y1u7BD">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1N64y1u7BD</a></p>
<h3 id="代码仓库">代码仓库</h3>
<p><a href="https://github.com/gongluck/Character-player/tree/console">https://github.com/gongluck/Character-player/tree/console</a></p>
<div class="highlight"><pre style="background-color:#eed;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4"><code class="language-C++" data-lang="C++"><span style="color:#1e889b">#include</span> <span style="color:#1e889b">&lt;iostream&gt;</span><span style="color:#1e889b">
</span><span style="color:#1e889b">#include</span> <span style="color:#1e889b">&lt;thread&gt;</span><span style="color:#1e889b">
</span><span style="color:#1e889b">#include</span> <span style="color:#1e889b">&lt;atomic&gt;</span><span style="color:#1e889b">
</span><span style="color:#1e889b"></span>
<span style="color:#1e889b">#ifdef _WIN32
</span><span style="color:#1e889b">#include</span> <span style="color:#1e889b">&lt;Windows.h&gt;</span><span style="color:#1e889b">
</span><span style="color:#1e889b">#define ssize_t SSIZE_T
</span><span style="color:#1e889b">#endif
</span><span style="color:#1e889b">#include</span> <span style="color:#1e889b">&lt;vlc/vlc.h&gt;</span><span style="color:#1e889b">
</span><span style="color:#1e889b"></span>
<span style="color:#1e889b">#define CHECKEQUALRET(ret, compare)\
</span><span style="color:#1e889b"></span><span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">if</span>(ret == compare)<span style="color:#a61717;background-color:#e3d2d2">\</span>
{<span style="color:#a61717;background-color:#e3d2d2">\</span>
